The hymn was again recorded by the orchestra of the National Theatre under the direction of Jiří Bělohlávek.
We have four versions - with a male or female solo song, a chorus interpretation and an instrumental version.
The song is provided by Kateřina Kněžínková and Adam Plachetka.
